cdata.name: Legends Cryptocurrency
cdata.desc: The Legends Cryptocurrency is a token issued on the Ethereum blockchain. It is used as a payment system within The Legends Room, a Las Vegas-based strip club. The token allows clients to receive additional discounts. 5000 tokens equals a membership in the club which allows clients to have a 50% discount on all in-club activities except gaming. The membership is valid for a lifetime and extends to one guest.
